      <h1 class="cs-title">Water-Wise Landscaping for Las Cruces</h1>
      <p class="cs-text">Xeriscaping isn't just rocks and gravel — it's a complete landscape approach designed to thrive with minimal water. We use drought-tolerant plants, native species, and efficient irrigation to create outdoor spaces that look great year-round while keeping your water bills low.</p>
      <p class="cs-text">Our xeriscape designs balance beauty with practicality. We select plants that are proven in the Las Cruces climate, group them by water needs, and install drip irrigation that delivers water exactly where it's needed.</p>
