      <span class="cs-topper">Why Xeriscape</span>
      <h2 class="cs-title">Save Water Without Sacrificing Curb Appeal</h2>
      <p class="cs-text">Southern New Mexico averages under 10 inches of rain per year. Traditional lawns and non-native plants struggle here — and they waste water doing it. Xeriscaping works with the climate instead of fighting it.</p>
      <p class="cs-text">Our clients typically see significant reductions in their water bills after a xeriscape installation. And because we use plants adapted to the desert, maintenance stays low. No more fighting to keep non-native species alive through July and August.</p>
